WEBVTT

00:00.541 --> 00:01.158
ï»¿Hello?

00:01.449 --> 00:03.567
Hi Amanda, what have you been doing?

00:04.125 --> 00:05.747
I've been working all day.

00:06.112 --> 00:07.341
What makes you so busy?

00:08.040 --> 00:09.905
My sister got married last year.

00:10.352 --> 00:12.720
She gave birth to a boy two days ago.

00:13.018 --> 00:14.584
Congratulations!

00:14.872 --> 00:15.609
Thank you.

00:15.955 --> 00:18.479
Now, I have three nieces and two nephews.

00:18.803 --> 00:19.778
I'm so happy.

00:20.003 --> 00:22.929
Wow, you have a lot of nieces and nephews.

00:23.244 --> 00:23.701
Yes.

00:23.987 --> 00:25.452
We are a large family.

00:25.630 --> 00:26.820
That's great!

00:27.115 --> 00:29.103
How many brothers and sisters do you have?

00:29.604 --> 00:32.056
I have one sister and two brothers.

00:32.398 --> 00:33.440
Did they all get married?

00:33.937 --> 00:37.369
Yes, that's why I have many nieces and nephews.

00:37.607 --> 00:39.235
Okay, that makes sense.

00:39.450 --> 00:42.139
My big brother has two daughters and a son.

00:42.656 --> 00:45.533
But my sister-in-law wants to have one more baby.

00:45.732 --> 00:46.449
Wow.

00:46.549 --> 00:48.323
She wants to have a big family, too.

00:48.740 --> 00:49.220
Yes.

00:49.705 --> 00:51.844
My sister-in-law was the only child.

00:52.380 --> 00:55.196
She said she always felt lonely when she was young.

00:55.561 --> 00:57.567
That's why she wants to have many children.

00:57.961 --> 00:58.882
I think so.

00:59.279 --> 01:02.909
Actually, I also want to have more nieces and nephews.

